Notes saving app [using command line] which saved notes in a JSON file and have multiple functionalities like 
1. Add Note
2. Remove Note
3. List of Notes
4. Read Specific Note

Commands to RUN:
1. node app.js add --title="Title" --body="Message"
2. node app.js remove --title="Title"
3. node app.js list
4. node app.js read --title="Title"

IMPORTANT NOTE
Before Running App type command "npm install" to fetch npm-modules required for running the app.
